<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TPal4">
<l>mēṭṭiḷa mētikaḷ taḷaiviṭu māyarkaḷ vēyṅkuḻa lōcaiyum viṭaimaṇik kuralu</l>
<l>mīṭṭiya vicaiticai parantaṉa vayaluḷ irintaṉa curumpiṉa milaṅkaiyar kulattai</l>
<l>vāṭṭiya varicilai vāṉava rēṟē māmuṉi vēḷviyaik kāttava pirata</l>
<l>māṭṭiya vaṭutiṟa layōttiyem maracē yaraṅkattam māpaḷḷi yeḻuntaru ḷāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The collective music of the sound of the bamboo flutes of the cowherds,</l>
<l>who untie [their] tall, young buffaloes, and the ringing of the bulls’ bells</l>
<l>have spread in [all] directions.</l>
<l>Swarms of bees in the paddy-fields have scampered away.</l>
<l>O Bull among celestials with a striped bow that scorched the Laṅkan people’s clans!</l>
<l>O our King of Ayodhyā with the might to kill [the foes],</l>
<l>Who protected the sacrifice of the great ascetic and</l>
<l>allowed [him] to have a bath at the completion of [his] sacrifice!</l>
<l>O Lord of Raṅgam, do grace to wake up from sleep!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
